USES:
1. Saves time
2. Responsive (Most powerful festure)
3. Easy to use - well documented, straight forward to learn
4. Customizable

FEATURES:
1. Mobile first philosophy
2. Grid system
3. Reusable components

COMPETITORS:
1. Foundation
2. Bulma
3. Taiwind CSS

Responsive vs Adaptive:
Responsive: A technique to make the web pages to render well in variety of device and sizes

Relative vs Static Units:
Static units: px, pt
Relative units: %, em, rem, vw, vh




